name: Colosseum
fullText:
Colosseum's demo day will be hosted virtually on Thursday this week.

The private event will feature pitches from the 10 most promising early-stage startups in the Solana eco who are part of our 3rd accelerator batch.

If you're an investor that would like to join, send us a DM. https://t.co/fG1Ix7zOYz
